text: Infinite is the debut studio album by American rapper Eminem. It was released on November 12, 1996. It was produced by Jeff & Mark Bass, Denaun Porter, DJ Head, Eminem and DJ Rec. The album was given 2.5 out of 5 stars by Allmusic. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:1996 albums Category:Debut albums Category:Eminem albums Category:Hip hop albums Category:Hip hop soul albums Category:R&B; albums
